{"version":1,"ops":[{"author":{"id":"9eb510892d1accc0c715d21128d216b2e6f74967"},"files":null,"message":"The 'event-queue' full situation needs to be handled both in the _frameserver\nside in the engine, and in the shmif-server implementation.\n\nIntended fix:\n1. in the normal poll-stage, check if there is a deferred notification, and\n   if so, re-attempt delivery\n\n2. if the event-queue is continuously full, try and poke the semaphore to\n   unblock an open client.\n\n3. better squishing of high-rate events, and migrate to mmio:ed mouse state.","timestamp":1559507454,"type":3}]}